Title: Kenzo Jungle Homme EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: When your life reaches a point where it starts and ends with the contents of your organiser, it’s time to shake things up. With just a whiff of Kenzo Jungle Homme, forget reason and routine, embrace reckless spontaneity and take part in the most exciting chapter of your life. Created for the explosive spirit under a veneer of dullness, this heady Eau De Toilette is made for the esteemed house of Kenzo. The top note opens with an explosion of citruses with zesty notes of lemon with sweet and slightly bitter bergamot against the fragrant spice of cinnamon with a dash of lime. Moving into the heart note, the warm smell of nutmeg, fragrant carnation, smoky notes of amber, sweet-spicy cardamom and bitter-tea notes of mate with the bite of pepper makes an emphatic statement. Finally, the base note reminds you of a warming hearth with tenacious rooty hints of vetiver, resinous benzoin similar to vanilla, warming cedar, rich and exotic notes of sandalwood and the mild tea-rose smell of guaiac wood. The aromatic essence of this luxury fragrance is ideal for those wild and spontaneous evenings that one day become cherished memories. The complex fragrance is housed in a simple bottle with a glass rectangular frame. A matte silver stopper flaunts an interesting crown of zebra-toned bristles. A spritz of this provocative scent from Kenzo will have you swinging from the vines, indulging your wild side.
